<br>
Get a phantom/skeleton/mist golem, lower lv you get will work better... bring it to the door fear it.....wait.<br>
<br>
Black reaver runs out, feign, stand (or get somone to tag) etc etc, i am sure you know res.<br>
<br>
Can also fear mobs to 'cause' adds hence efficently pulling all the goo from the skywalk in batches.<br>
<br>
<br>
Take agro pulling in pog, get sow+invis, run to tunare's tree, agro a trent, run back feign, run and agro the named if you can : Ghral, Sarik, Feyl etc... run back to zone. Use multiple feigns to get back without adds.<br>
     Now you have agro any aything the named mobs pass, but because they are out of range wont attack you.<br>
<br>
Basically you wander neer a mob and they agro you from miles away, can pull in 2-4's depending on how slop you are, plenty of single....but this is around 5x faster than bard pulling, because mobs agro as soon as they are on your clip range, so you can strongly dictate what comes to you... as you dont have to go and whack it.<br>
Very fast way of pulling, never seen anything so fast!  <p><img src="http://eqsighost.netfirms.com/Braellarth/sig_02.jpg"><br></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1>Firiona Vie General Chat</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.0.8<br>Copyright ©1999-2002 ezboard, Inc.<br>Accelerated By <a href=http://www.wbs.com/ezboard.html>JXEL</a></center></body></html>  

